WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.766 --> 00:00:05.233
How is my granddaughter?

2
00:00:05.266 --> 00:00:07.500
The patient is temporarily out of danger

3
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.300
Only his waist was seriously injured

4
00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:10.766
Uterine injuries are more serious

5
00:00:10.766 --> 00:00:12.900
It will be more difficult for him to have children in the future

6
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.900
You mean he will be infertile in the future?

7
00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:16.166
Then it will definitely not be born

8
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:18.633
Doctor, I don't want to know if he can have children

9
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:20.766
I just want to know if he'll get better. Don't worry.

10
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:22.800
We will do our best to treat

11
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.233
Please be patient.

12
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.266
Brother, you haven't slept all night

13
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:28.466
Morning

14
00:00:28.466 --> 00:00:31.000
Madam will be very distressed to see you like this

15
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.900
As long as he doesn't wake up

16
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:34.633
I didn't dare to close my eyes for a moment

17
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:35.966
I'm afraid I'll close my eyes

18
00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:37.166
He won't wake up

19
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:39.566
The doctor has already said that he is out of danger

20
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:41.166
Don't be so nervous anymore

21
00:00:41.266 --> 00:00:42.700
He was unconscious for so long

22
00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:44.200
Must be scared

23
00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:47.833
I imagine him seeing me the first time he opens his eyes

24
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:51.766
XinYue

